                <h2 class="fs-96 roboto fw-600 first">Lift off.</h2>
                <p class="fs-16 metropolis-light second">Using atomic programmatic principles, combined with separation of concerns allows us to successfully create, change and deploy our code with ease. Minimising the risk of unwanted behaviour; whilst creating projects that scale effectivly.</p>
