                    <div  class="title-space" x-data x-show="$store.theme.current === 'space'">
                        <h2 class="fs-96 roboto fw-600 first">At the speed of light.</h2>
                        <p class="fs-32 metropolis-light second">We ensure that we make the most of quick deployments and scalable code.</p>
                        <p class="fs-16 metropolis-light third">We separate our logic layer from our view layer; and utilise middleware on our data leaving the database to create highly flexible functionality which runs smooth, fast and is painless to upgrade, change or extend.</p>
                        
